      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FERRYFORTH MARY (2) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three on end. Last start rocketed out of the boxes with a scorching early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (31.50) at this track over 500m. Can measure up this time. FREEDOM VESTA (3) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (31.38) at this track in an A6. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. JAYMIR RUBY (5) had been in super honest form hitting the frame four times on end before finishing fifth (18.41) at this track last time. Goes well out of this box with a win and nine minor placings. A big run wouldn't surprise. HONOUR PROMISE (4) collected a minor prize last start after leading - must be considered.",
